data.description: Make the most of every square foot! Welcome home, vaulted ceilings invite you into the large living area which opens to the dining area and kitchen. Maple cabinets with pull out shelving, pantry and tons of counter space perfect for the avid chef or growing family. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the main floor and an updated powder bath for guests. Upstairs boasts 3 bedrooms and a recently updated primary bathroom complete with double sinks, custom shower and walk in closet. Enjoy your finished basement great for a rec area or additonal family room, 3/4 bath and light and airy 4th bedroom. This beauty sits on a large corner lot, fully fenced, extended back patio, pergola with a hot tub and much more!
